    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car is in absolutely flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been pampered in a garage its whole life and drives like a dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
