    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This garage-kept masterpiece features a flawless exterior with deep, lustrous paint entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the factory alloy wheels are pristine, showing zero curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no visible wear on the bolsters, and the 'new car' scent persists. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with every scheduled maintenance performed by certified technicians. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, reflecting the meticulous care this vehicle has received. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a turn-key example that requires absolutely nothing but a new home.",
